results.title: T'was a Dark and Stormy Night...
results.description: At Alistaire's Birthday party, Meggan transforms into a vampire and Excalibur calls Dr. Strange in for help.

results.title: No Man Is an Island (But No Island Is a Man Either So It Works Out)
results.description: Nightcrawler flies off for a little R&R but crash lands on an island that is the home of (I'm NOT making this up) the Son of Krakoa, The Living Island (from Giant-Size X-Men #1); Mayhem and general silliness ensues.

results.title: Someone Will Die For This
results.description: Kitty enrolls in an exclusive prep-school where she has a very hard time fitting in.

results.title: Cat on a Hot Tin Roof
results.description: Mesmero mesmerizes Excalibur to save his own skin; Kitty and her classmates decide to try out as cheerleaders to make enough money so that they can keep their school from closing down.

results.title: School Spirit (or Cheerleaders From Heck)
results.description: With the help of Excalibur, Mesmero draws Fenris out into the open; Kitty and her cheerleading squad help her teammates take down the bad guys; The girl's school is saved and Kitty returns to Excalibur.

results.title: Heartbreaker
results.description: Excalibur desperately tries to find an abducted girl; Rachel is sent on a dark mind trip when she finds the girl guarded by D'Spayre.

results.title: X's and O's
results.description: Brian returns to his old research facility to quell a protest against the lab's illegal experiments and discovers his old mentor is a version of Arnim Zola; Excalibur faces down the Outlaws when Sable brings her team in to recover stolen equiptment.

results.title: The Promethium Exchange Book One: House Call
results.description: Dr. Doom tricks Kitty into taking him to Limbo and giving him access to the Soulsword so he can turn the whole place into promethium; The Lady of the Lake calls in the Avengers West Coast to help Excalibur stop his nefarious plot.

results.title: The Promethium Exchange Book Two: Out On A Limbo
results.description: The Lady of the Lake sends the Avengers West Coast into Limbo to help Excalibur stop Dr. Doom and save England.

results.title: The Promethium Exchange Book Three: Heart Of The Matter
results.description: Excalibur, Avengers West Coast and Darkoth face down Dr. Doom for the fate of Limbo, England and the World; Doom is beaten but gains promethium armor; Darkoth becomes protector of Limbo (now called Otherplace).

results.title: At Last...The Reunion !
